the location of the convocation center will
be made until all of the studies are com-
plete.

Two of the convocation center locations
would keep the building on the upper part
of Pitt’s campus, where most university ath-
letic facilities are already located. These
sites include the OC lot adjacent to the Pitt
Stadium and the football practice field

behind the Cost Center.

