the stadium comes the possibility of con-
necting Trees Hall, Fitzgerald Field House
and Salk Hall through the convocation cen-
ter in addition to a concourse joining it
to the stadium. A possible complication
with the OC lot proposal is the current
presence of several fraternity houses at the
site.

